## 3.4 Walkthrough 4 тАФ Static Block Execution Order

```java
class Demo {
    static int a = 10;
    static int b;

    // First static block
    static {
        System.out.println("Static Block 1 executed");
        b = a * 4;
    }

    // Second static block
    static {
