## 4. Structural Diagrams & Schematics

### 4.1 Mermaid Class Hierarchy тАФ Multilevel Inheritance

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Vehicle {
        +String brand
        +int speed
        +start() void
        +stop() void
    }
    class Car {
        +int numberOfDoors
        +playMusic() void
        +start() void
    }
    class ElectricCar {
        +int batteryCapacity
        +charge() void
    }
    Vehicle <|-- Car
    Car <|-- ElectricCar
```

**Reading the diagram:**

- `Vehicle` is the root superclass.
