### 4.2 Mermaid Block Diagram тАФ Object Construction Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Source Code Compilation javac] --> B[Bytecode Verification]
    B --> C[ClassLoader Subsystem]
    C --> D[Superclass Class Loaded into Method Area]
    C --> E[Subclass Class Loaded into Method Area]
