### Execution Trace for `new SportsCar();`

The derivation of the call order proceeds as follows:

$$
\text{Call Stack: } \text{SportsCar}() \xrightarrow{\text{super()}} \text{Car}() \xrightarrow{\text{super()}} \text{Vehicle}() \xrightarrow{\text{super()}} \text{Object}()
$$

| Step | Method Executed | Console Output |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `Object()` (implicit) | *(no output)* |
| 2 | `Vehicle()` body | `Vehicle constructor` |
| 3 | `Car()` body | `Car constructor` |
| 4 | `SportsCar()` body | `SportsCar constructor` |

