### **Question 1** `[KTU University Exam тАУ May 2024]`
**What is constructor chaining? Explain how it is achieved in Java with an example.**

**Model Answer (3 marks):**
Constructor chaining is the process of calling one constructor from another constructor. In Java, it is achieved using two keywords:
