**[KTU University Exam тАФ Dec 2023, Model Paper]**

**(a)** Differentiate between abstract class and concrete class in Java. Explain with suitable examples. **(7 marks)**

**(b)** Design a Java program using an abstract class `Vehicle` with abstract method `speed()`. Create two subclasses `Car` and `Bike` that override `speed()` to return their maximum speeds. Demonstrate the use of an array of `Vehicle` references to call `speed()` polymorphically. **(7 marks)**

