            String name = u[0];
            int age = Integer.parseInt(u[1]);
            try {
                System.out.println("Attempting to register " + name + "...");
                register(name, age);
            } catch (InvalidAgeException e) {
                System.out.println("Custom Exception Caught: " + e.getMessage());
            } finally {
                System.out.println("  [Log: registration attempt completed for " + name + "]");
            }
        }
    }
}
```

**Expected Output:**
```
