  [Log: registration attempt completed for Alice]
Attempting to register Bob...
Custom Exception Caught: Bob is underage (15). Registration denied.
  [Log: registration attempt completed for Bob]
Attempting to register Carol...
Carol registered successfully.
  [Log: registration attempt completed for Carol]
Attempting to register Dave...
Custom Exception Caught: Dave is underage (12). Registration denied.
  [Log: registration attempt completed for Dave]
```

**Key Points for Valuation:**
- `InvalidAgeException` **extends `Exception`** (checked). **(1 mark)**
- `register` method **declares `throws InvalidAgeException`** in signature. **(1 mark)**
- `throw` uses a **single object** of the custom class. **(1 mark)**
- `try-catch-finally` correctly wraps the call. **(2 marks)**
- Program compiles and produces expected output. **(2 marks)**

