**Summary table for the answer:**

| Constructor | Input | Result |
|---|---|---|
| `String()` | none | `""` |
| `String(String)` | another String | A copy |
| `String(char[])` | char array | Full char-to-String |
| `String(char[], int, int)` | char array with offset/count | Substring from char array |
| `String(byte[])` | byte array | Decoded with platform charset |
| `String(byte[], int, int, String)` | byte array with charset | Decoded subarray |
| `String(StringBuffer)` | StringBuffer | Immutable snapshot |
| `String(StringBuilder)` | StringBuilder | Immutable snapshot |

