## 2.6 KTU Formula Sheet / Cheat Sheet

| Concept | Method Signature | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Register listener | `component.addXxxListener(XxxListener l)` | Always lowercase 'xxx' |
| Remove listener | `component.removeXxxListener(XxxListener l)` | Optional cleanup |
| Get event source | `e.getSource()` | Returns `Object` |
| Get event command | `e.getActionCommand()` | Returns `String` label |
| Get key character | `e.getKeyChar()` | For `KeyEvent` |
| Get key code | `e.getKeyCode()` | For `KeyEvent` (e.g., `VK_ENTER`) |
| Get mouse coords | `e.getX()`, `e.getY()` | Relative to component |
| Get modifiers | `e.getModifiers()` | For `MouseEvent` (e.g., `BUTTON1_DOWN_MASK`) |
