### Question B (14 Marks) тАФ **[KTU University Exam тАУ June 2024]**

**(a)** Differentiate between `MouseListener` and `MouseMotionListener` interfaces. Write a program to change the background color of a panel when the mouse is dragged across it. **(7 marks)**

